column2: SELECT m.NAME, m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1, n.objid, n.distance, m.RMAG, m.BMAG, m.REDSHIFT, m.BROAD_TYPE, m.OPTICAL_FLAG, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.err_u, o.err_g, o.err_r, o.err_i, o.err_z, o.SpecObjID, o.mode FROM MyDB.milliquas AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid WHERE m.REDSHIFT > # AND o.clean = #
